<h4><a href="https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-pro-rata">苹果否认对收购 TikTok 感兴趣</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356592" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TikTok-owner-ByteDance-planning-streaming-music-service-768x384.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>多个信源告诉 Axios，苹果对收购 TikTok 表示感兴趣，但强调暂时没有苹果内部信源确认这个消息。随后，苹果发言人告诉 Axios，苹果内部没有讨论收购 TikTok 该事宜，公司也对此不感兴趣。</p>
<p>如果苹果真的收购 TikTok，这将成为其金额最大的一笔收购。目前其最大收购为以 30 亿美元收购 Beats，而《The Information》表示 TikTok 估值可以去到 300 亿美元或更高。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1011221.htm">华为 Mate 40 Pro 渲染图曝光</a></h4>
<p>快科技消息，oneleaks 分享了华为 Mate 40 和 Mate 40 Pro 的渲染图。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356594" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-4.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-4.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1-4-360x240.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>从图中可见，Mate 40 采用双曲面挖孔屏，挖孔在左上角。背部是圆形四摄，侧边的实体电源、音量键均得到保留。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356593" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Mate 40 Pro 的曲率较高，背部同样采用圆形四摄，其中一颗为方形潜望式变焦镜头，顶部暂不确认是 3.5mm 耳机孔还是红外发射预留。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356595" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro.jpg" alt="" width="1986" height="977" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro.jpg 1986w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro-360x177.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro-768x378.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/pro-1024x504.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1986px) 100vw, 1986px" /></p>
<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/4/21354593/mulan-release-date-disney-earnings-warner-bros-tenet-theaters">《花木兰》将于 Disney+ 首映</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356596" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg.jpeg" alt="" width="2500" height="1547" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg.jpeg 2500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg-360x223.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg-768x475.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1_NFrkkczXC1pKlbLkJ-wgIg-1024x634.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，迪士尼真人电影《花木兰》将于 9 月 4 日在迪士尼流媒体 Disney+ 首映，想观看的订阅用户需额外支付 29.9 美元的费用。官方表示，Disney+ 订阅用户已经超过六千万。</p>
<p>迪士尼 CEO Bob Chapek 补充，在 Disney+ 尚未上线的市场，迪士尼将于同一日期在电影院上映《花木兰》，目前暂无关于中国市场定档相关的确切消息。</p>
